      <hedline>
        <hl1>Stateless No More</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Statelessness is alive and well in Europe (Week in Review, April 8). Despite 40 years of being a Bosnian, after being ''ethnically cleansed'' from our Sarajevo home at the beginning of the Bosnian civil war and then erased from government records, my family and I now celebrate the day when we arrived in the United States and became -- in our hearts, and soon thereafter in American government records -- nonhyphenated Americans.</p>
        <p>Ray Miles  Dallas, April 8, 2007</p>
      </block>
